						.col.col-md-4.col--testimonial
							.testimonial--card
								img.img-responsive.testimonial--logo(src="../img/logos/covermymeds.png" alt="Cover My Meds logo")
								p.testimonial--body "NAI Ohio Equities provided valuable and frequent updates on real estate market conditions, deals in play, whose word can be trusted, etc. Also, it was clear throughout our process that other persons and organizations hold Ohio Equities generally in high regard as knowledgeable and trustworthy counter-parties. Through their reputation, we gained a huge benefit in others assuming at the outset that we were a worthy, albeit small, organization."
								p.testimonial--source - Alan Scantland, CEO
